2013-01-01|2013-12-30.description: Alfred knew that deferring maintenance on the Bat-wing was dangerous, but even he didn't expect it to fail so completely. Will he receive good news from the downed plane before Wayne Foundation stock plummets even more disastrously? "Return of Batman" part 2.
2013-01-01|2013-12-30.name: Return of Batman, Part 2 of 4

2013-01-01|2013-12-30.description: Lois discovered the secret Lex has been keeping, and she turns to Otis for confirmation. But it's not unti a certain visitor from Gotham makes the scene that she knows for sure! Meanwhilte, Emil's plan to save Vegas from the Black Flash takes a risky turn, as hyper-charged Superman faces the deadly menace on his own.
2013-01-01|2013-12-30.name: Haunted Part 9

2013-01-01|2013-12-30.description: There's only enough room for one Green Hornet and Kato in Century City! One Green Hornet is back from the dead, the other is loathe to let go of his mantle. The legacy of the emerald insect looms large over this battle to the death. Did we mention a dirty bomb is poised to go off and the city hangs in the balance?

It ends where it began, in the heart of Hyrkania itself. Red Sonja is queen no more, but before she is done with the realm of crowns and kings, there is royal blood yet to be spilled, and her homeland yet to free.
With the help of an ancient force, New father Prophet searches for a weapon to fight a deadly threat to the Empire.

2013-01-01|2013-12-30.description:
NIGHT OF THE SYMBIOTE SLAYERS!

It's Eddie Brock and Flash Thompson fighting side by side for the city of Philadelphia!

Lives are at stake, a conspiracy revealed - and two lunatics with Alien parasites to the rescue!
2013-01-01|2013-12-30.name: Night of the Symbiote Slayers!

"Sacrifices" part 1 of 2. After the shocking events of the season one finale, Oliver reflects on the regrets of his past...and his course of action for the future.

2013-01-01|2013-12-30.description: The Prophecy Has Been Fulfilled! The Dragon has been reborn! The Dark One has been dealt a great blow, and the people of the world rejoice, finally, in the coming of spring! It has been a long journey for Rand al'Thor and his friends, and it has changed them all forever. Join us now for the conclusion to this adaptation of Robert Jordan's epic fantasy, The WHEEL OF TIME: THE EYE OF THE WORLD!

volume.name: Robert Jordan's Wheel of Time: The Eye of the World

2013-01-01|2013-12-30.description:
Fan favorite Crossed writer, DAVID LAPHAM, turns up the crazy to insane levels in the continuing tale of Psychopath survivor, Amanda. Alone and at the mercy of the strange religious tribal Crossed she fights both to survive and to keep the rising tide of mental anguish threatening to push her permanently over the edge into madness.

Available with a Regular cover by Miguel Ruiz, Torture cover by Michael Dipascale, Wraparound cover by Gabriel Andrade, and a special Red Crossed Incentive also by Ruiz.

THE HELLFIRE SAGA CONCLUDES!

Wolverine and the X-Men face Mystique, Sabretooth and the Hellfire Club!

What fate awaits the Jean Grey School students who joined the New Hellions?

The WOLVERINE AND THE X-MEN landscape is redefined!

2013-01-01|2013-12-30.description: It's a deadly showdown between Batman and Superman--two former best friends now turned deadly enemies. Batman has run out of time to replicate the pill that will give anyone Godlike powers. He's about to pay a terrible price.
2013-01-01|2013-12-30.name: Chapter 35

2013-01-01|2013-12-30.description: Traffic lights stop working, machines are broken--networked devices all over Europe are compromised, just like the network in THE 99's own headquarters last issue! Whatever was in THE 99's system has found its way into the wider world. Meanwhile, Aleem has a vision--THE 99, all lying as if dead inside their own training bunker! THE JUNIOR 99 act, in secret, to investigate. But when newcomer Raheema the Merciful takes over the team from Jabbar's sister Noaf, will her mistake spell doom for the team, including Dr. Ramzi? Also, in back-up story FIRST CONTACT, Jami, Mumita, and Hafiz try to stop farm machinery running amok--and finally, Jami ties in the energy signature to one they're seen before--when they were searching for a rocket in outer space!

Is Archie a man or a mouse? He'll let you know after he asks Veronica! Feeling annoyed at everyone's assumption that he's "henpecked" by his spoiled sweetheart, Archie's determined to show that he can do things on his own. Can he prove himself an independent man? Or will he be walking on thin ice? Find out in "Deep Freeze!"
